staging: mt7621-pci: remove 'RALINK_PCI_BAR0SETUP_ADDR' definition

Instead of define RALINK_PCI_BAR0SETUP_ADDR just use standard
pci defnition for this which is 'PCI_BASE_ADDRESS_0'.

